comments.content: [Humanist Slabserif 712 BT Bold](http://web.archive.org/web/20080708213434/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/bitstream/humanist-slabserif-712/bold/) appears to be a match.
The numerals are Univers, the rest is Egyptienne.
